# Single source of truth for container image versions.
# For each image prefix (e.g., SPLUNK, UF, PROM, GRAFANA), define:
#   <PREFIX>_IMAGE_REPO   = registry/repo path
#   EITHER
#     <PREFIX>_IMAGE_TAG    = tag (dev-friendly)
#   OR
#     <PREFIX>_IMAGE_DIGEST = sha256:... (prod/CI pinned)
#
# IMPORTANT: Do NOT set both TAG and DIGEST for the same prefix.
# The resolver will generate <PREFIX>_IMAGE=<repo:tag|repo@sha256:...>
# which compose should reference as ${<PREFIX>_IMAGE}.
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Optional: default registry (unused by resolver unless you incorporate it)
